devdoc.details: Unsigned math operations with safety checks that revert on error

add(uint256,uint256).details: Adds two unsigned integers, reverts on overflow.

div(uint256,uint256).details: Integer division of two unsigned integers truncating the quotient, reverts on division by zero.

mod(uint256,uint256).details: Divides two unsigned integers and returns the remainder (unsigned integer modulo), reverts when dividing by zero.
